The lack of snow in mountain bothers hoteliers 
The deserted pose no problem that operators of ski lifts. 
The lack of snow discourages people to book their stays in skiing in hotels and pensions. 
It is always possible to find free rooms for all dates in winter, including Christmas and New Year. 
We have a lot of visits on our site. 
Internet users roam the offers, asking prices but dare not commit to reserve for the moment. 
And if they call, they ask immediately if there will be snow or mud at Christmas, "said Martin Jandura, operator of the information portal Spindl. Info. 
If you want to spend the New year of his dreams to špindlerův Mlýn, better not too reluctant to book. 
If the priority is given to economies and that the quality of accommodation only then, then we can try to wait a few more days. 
The Hoteliers of špindler propose for the moment that stays a week for the New Year. 
I think they will try again a moment of the place, but they cèderont them and accept shorter periods. 
And then the number of rooms free will rapidly diminish, "said Jandura. 
The tourism agency Ingtours of Vrchlabí also proposes still beds of free for all periods of winter. 
The week of Christmas we are most concerned for the moment, it is not completely sold. 
There are still free, say, half the rooms in our offer. 
That is why we have already prepared a few stays Christmas last-minute cheaper, "said the director of Ingtours Petr Schiefert. 
The agency of tourism agency may also propose The New year to Krkonoše, but there are fewer empty seats. 
The 14 days of February go well, the remaining winter stays are moderately. 
This year, the interest for stays of winter has been negatively influenced by the fact that there is still no snow to Krkonoše. 
People expect it to get to fall. 
Nobody wants to spend the winter in the mountains without snow. 
If the tracks overlap during the week, Christmas also will be complete, "think Schiefert. 
In contrast, the occupation of the hotel Horizont Pec pod Sněžkou is slightly higher than last year. 
It was an improvement of about five percent. 
We have few places for the New Year as for Christmas. 
There is a great interest during the holidays of Polish January and February sells well too, "said Karel Rada, director of the best hotel of Pec. 
The Omnia Hotel near the central parking of Jánské Lázně is also full to eighty percent during the period of the New Year. 
On the contrary, half the beds remain empty at Christmas in the most recent hotel Jánské Lázně. 
This year, we were pleasantly surprised by the month of January, where we have already sixty percent of occupation at present. 
February is a little more low at the moment, but as soon as the snow will fall, the interest for stays in the Krkonoše builds certainly still indicated the director of the hotel Omnia, Erik Sporysch. 
The Hotel of Krkonoše should not expect more snow. 
On Thursday it will be fresher and if there is precipitation, they should be neigeuses mountain. 
But the time should warm, informed Jiří Jakubský station Hradec Czech Hydrometeorological Institute. 
United States: repetition is mother of wisdom 
It becomes even comical, the painstaking effort with which Barack Obama, president the reputation of wise, reproduced the strategy of his predecessor on the Afghan question, that he considered himself as simple. 
When he eventually leave sweat its doctrine so eagerly awaited, it turned out that he had recopied carbon paper since the Iraq scenario of Bush three years ago. 
Not content to use in the text several times the expression "as in Iraq, it has not hesitated, moreover, to use the title of Bush's speech of January 2007 as the title of his own speech:" A new way forward " 
At the same time, he has personally criticized the idea of Bush to send new reinforcements in Iraq consumed by the civil war as "irresponsible and a disastrous decision in its consequences." 
The following month, however, have shown that the strategy of Bush, who came from the recommendations of commanders of campaigns, was the only possible and likely success to the point that the newspapers currently do not speak at all of Iraq. 
This has not improved the reputation of Bush, however, objectively speaking, it has left his successor a final situation much more favourable than we might hope. 
Barack Obama hope that in Afghanistan, the miracle will happen again 
It is again the commanders of campaigns that have requested an increase in the military contingent, including the Afghan operation commander, General Stanley McCristal, which has severely criticised the reluctance of the White House despite the habits of subordination. 
He asked 40 000 men in order to make the situation more favourable. 
The president has hesitated for three months but in the absence of a better option, at least he had defrauded the general of 10 000 soldiers. 
He has managed to root out the promise of 5, 000 additional from Europe, even if it were on 10 000. 
This brings the most problems throughout the strategy of Obama seems to be its intention to withdraw the armies of Afghanistan by 18 months and to complete the whole process within three years. The doctrine of Obama brings more questions than it provides answers. 
Many doubt the fact that an increase of half will bring the same fruit that progress in Iraq. 
In spite of fratricidal wars of recent years, Iraqi society is relatively well organised and its leaders to honour the agreements. 
The Afghan situation stands by the exact opposite - we cannot rely on person and no treaty is respected. 
In these conditions, difficult to prepare Afghan security forces, accustomed to change leader from day to day depending on what suits them. 
The political institutions, although based officially, will remain just window-dressing behind which will proliferate patriarchal ethnic relations. 
It is particularly complex to balance the interests of various ethnic groups given the lack of clarity about the reports, which are further complicated by the Pakistani and Iranian influences. 
Even the foundation of a "state quick to act ", which is the aim of the operation, does not seem to be very real. 
The time horizon of Obama's strategy makes perplexed by his determination. 
In the past eight years, the situation in Afghanistan has worsened and she is currently on the brink of chaos. 
Only a heart purely romantic and out of the reality can be persuaded that the small soldiers sent in the tumult of the war for their "prompt return home" will bring a real miracle. 
From a political point of view, set a date for the withdrawal of troops is purely irresponsible because the Taliban will regard as the indirect admission of defeat. 
The last NATO summit has shown that the will of Europeans to participate in military operations in Afghanistan is moving towards the negative. 
European politicians know or do not want to explain to their constituents what security in Germany or Italy is linked to a war in the mountains of the Hindu Kush. 
Another factor that can radically alter the situation is the development of events related to Iran. 
If the situation continues to deteriorate and that the sanctions have no effect on the Iranians, the Americans will face the very difficult issue of a resolution of the problem by the use of military force. 
It will respond by example when, according to Obama, America will come to the victorious withdrawal of troops from Afghanistan. 
Each solution of this type will, however, a dramatic reversal of the Afghan situation. 
The only patch for Obama is the fact that there are three years until the presidential elections and therefore there is still enough time to working on a new strategy, should it prove to be a flop. 
The leaders of the bank Goldman Sachs will no longer receive bonuses in cash 
Employees senior leaders of the U.S. bank Goldman Sachs will no longer receive cash bonuses this year. 
The company announced in response to strong criticism about its pay practices. 
The group of 30 key leaders will receive shares instead of money, they will not sell before five years. 
The actions can be withdrawn to leaders in cases where they would take too many risks. 
According to Reuters, Goldman Sachs raises leading the effort to link the rewards with long-term performance on Wall Street. 
I assume that Wall Street is well aware of the global sense that we must take, "said the former investment banker Douglas Elliott of JPMorgan society 
The concern is in the details, he added. 
The bank Goldman Sachs has become the target of criticism after being set aside almost $17 billion in premiums on the first three quarters of this year. 
For the current year, the total amount of premiums will probably exceed $20 billion despite the measure announced today, according to Reuters. 
With the arrival of the financial crisis, large bonuses in the banking sector have become a sensitive political issue in many countries. 
Britain announced Wednesday that it would affect a single fee of 50% bankers' bonuses exceeding 25, 000 pounds. 
France is preparing similar measures. 
This year women received the Nobel Prize in all areas except the physical 
These are five women, a record number, which have received today in Stockholm at the hands of the King of Sweden Charles XVI Gustave the Nobel Prize in technical disciplines and literature. 
In addition to the four scientists there was also the German writer of Romanian origin Herta Müller. 
Two American biologists, Elizabeth Blackburn and Carol Greider received with their compatriot Jack Szostak the Nobel Prize for Medicine for their research in the field of chromosomes. 
The prize for chemistry was awarded to the Israeli Ada Jonath with the Americans Venkatraman Ramakrishnan and Thomas Steitz for clarifying the structure and function of ribosomes 
The last winner received the Nobel Prize in Economics, U.S. Elinor Ostrom with his countryman Oliver Williamson, for their analysis of economic governance. 
The only technical discipline that has not been winner this year was The physical. 
This award was presented today scientists Charles Kao for his research in the field of optical fibres and George Smith avecWillard Boyle for their invention of CCD chips, which are currently at the basis of all digital cameras, fax or refracting telescopes. 
Each winner received the diploma, the Nobel medal and certificate of acquisition of financial reward. 
It reached 10 million Swedish kronor in each category. (approximately 1.1 million euros) 
If one of them has several winners, they will share the reward them. 
The much-anticipated Nobel Peace Prize has already been handed this afternoon in Oslo in Norway to U.S. President Barack Obama. 
In his speech, acknowledged the controversial nature of his award since it is only at the beginning of his journey and that it is in addition to the head of a country engaged in two wars in Iraq and Afghanistan. 
In the discharge of its policy he added that in certain situations the war is essential to achieve peace, even if the price is high. 
