The appointment of Kallen to the position of CEO of editions Burda is an intermediate solution: over the longer term, Hubert Burda hopes that his two children resume the press group, he told the newspaper Spiegel. 
The holding company must remain 100% a family business. 
Hamburg - A long term, the publisher Hubert Burda sees his company in the hands of its children 
