It does not depending predictable and apprehended (summary biographical, life and work), but by seeking something similar to the core of ignition of character created. 
The trip is exciting and Vincent spares neither fear nor the illuminations. 
Delicious pleasure, this book is also an invitation moving to readings and reviews. 
I leave you here a few snapshots. 
